OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FThe Middle East war has entered its
OL,7,Feighth day as an American bomber
OL,8,Flanded in Britain amid US warnings of
OL,9,Fa "surge" in strikes on Iran.
OL,11,FThe 146ft B-1 Lancer arrived at RAF
OL,12,FFairford in Gloucestershire on Friday
OL,13,Fevening after Sir Keir Starmer granted
OL,14,Fpermission for "defensive" US action
OL,15,Fagainst Iranian missile sites from UK
OL,16,Fbases.
OL,26,@qD@COUqD@IO]vD@POUvD@ZO]
