OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FA second Government charter flight
OL,7,Fcarrying British citizens from Oman
OL,8,Flanded at Gatwick Airport at 12.30am
OL,9,Fon Saturday as efforts to help people
OL,10,Ftrapped in the war zone continue.
OL,12,FThe Titan Airways flight departed from
OL,13,FMuscat International Airport at 5.30pm
OL,14,Fbefore a short layover in Cairo, Egypt.
OL,16,FThe latest arrivals join around 6,500
OL,17,FBritons who have returned from the
OL,18,FUnited Arab Emirates since widespread
OL,19,Fconflict began in the region.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
