OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FOn Saturday morning, Emirates
OL,7,Fannounced it was suspending all
OL,8,Fflights to and from Dubai after blasts
OL,9,Fwere reportedly heard in the city.
OL,11,FAbout 30 minutes later, the airline
OL,12,Fsaid flights would resume, with
OL,13,Fpassengers who have confirmed bookings
OL,14,Ffor flights that afternoon told they
OL,15,Fmay go to the airport.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FDubai International Airport said in a
OL,7,Fpost on X that operations had
OL,8,Fpartially resumed after the
OL,9,Fsuspension, but urged people not to
OL,10,Ftravel to the airport unless they had
OL,11,Fbeen contacted by their airline
OL,12,Fconfirming the flight.
OL,14,FQuestions linger over the UK's future
OL,15,Frole in the conflict, with Foreign
OL,16,FSecretary David Lammy suggesting RAF
OL,17,Fjets could legally strike Iranian
OL,18,Fmissile sites being used to attack
OL,19,FBritish interests in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
