OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FIn a call with Saudi Arabia's de facto
OL,7,Fleader Mohammed bin Salman on Friday,
OL,8,Fthe Prime Minister said the UK stands
OL,9,Fready to help defend the country
OL,10,Fshould it be needed.
OL,12,FIt comes after Britain was criticised
OL,13,Fby allies over its response to the
OL,14,Fcrisis, particularly over the defence
OL,15,Fof Cyprus, where a UK base was struck
OL,16,Fby a drone earlier this week.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
