OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch will renew
OL,7,Fher attack on the UK's response to the
OL,8,Fwar in a speech on Saturday, when she
OL,9,Fis expected to say that "allies feel
OL,10,Fthey can no longer rely on us".
OL,12,FSir Keir has defended his decision not
OL,13,Fto permit America to use British bases
OL,14,Fin the opening assault against the
OL,15,FTehran regime, suggesting it could
OL,16,Fhave been unlawful and arguing the
OL,17,FGovernment must keep a "cool head."
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@^O]yD@XOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister agreed on Sunday to
OL,7,Fallow the US to strike Iran
OL,8,Fdefensively from Fairford and Diego
OL,9,FGarcia, an island in the Indian Ocean.
OL,11,FUS defence secretary Pete Hegseth has
OL,12,Fwarned that strikes were "about to
OL,13,Fsurge dramatically", referring to
OL,14,F"more fighter squadrons, more
OL,15,Fdefensive capabilities and more bomber
OL,16,Fpulses more frequently."
OL,26,@tD@ZOUuD@SO]vD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773079565
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in Gloucestershire as
OL,4,CIran war enters eighth day
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump demanded Iran's
OL,7,F"unconditional surrender" as Israeli
OL,8,Fwarplanes pounded Tehran and Beirut
OL,9,Fand Iran launched another wave of
OL,10,Fretaliatory strikes against Israel and
OL,11,FGulf countries on Friday.
OL,13,FMore flights to the UK are expected to
OL,14,Fbe announced over the coming days.
OL,16,FQatar Airways said on Friday evening
OL,17,Fthat it would operate a "limited
OL,18,Frelief corridor" with flights from
OL,19,FDoha on Saturday to Heathrow, Paris,
OL,20,FMadrid, Rome and Frankfurt.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@YO]yD@YOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
